String.Source: I'm not making any promises, but I'll keep it in mind.

String.Source: You keep talking like this, you're the one that's going to end up in the ground.

String.Source: Of course, I understand. Still taking it all in.

String.Source: Oh! Uh... hello, boss! Congratulations on taking out Colter... I'm, uh... sure you'll do great.
String.Dest: Oh! Uh... hello, boss! Congratulations on taking out Colter... I'm, uh... sure you'll do great.

String.Source: Well, to be honest, I don't know you yet, boss.
String.Dest: Well, to be honest, I don't know you yet, boss.

String.Source: Sorry I'm so nervous, I don't mean any disrespect, boss. I just don't know where I stand with you and I don't want to end up pissing you off.
String.Dest: Sorry I'm so nervous, I don't mean any disrespect, boss. I just don't know where I stand with you and I don't want to end up pissing you off.

String.Source: I'm still trying to figure out if I even want this gig.
String.Dest: I'm still trying to figure out if I even want this gig.

String.Source: Why would you congratulate me? It's not like you're free to go.
String.Dest: Why would you congratulate me? It's not like you're free to go.

String.Source: What's your problem?
String.Dest: Co máš za problém?

String.Source: Lose the atittude, or lose something a lot more valuable.
String.Dest: Lose the atittude, or lose something a lot more valuable.

String.Source: Nothing like that. I'm just having a look around.
String.Dest: Nothing like that. I'm just having a look around.

String.Source: No offense intended. I know it's a tough job.
String.Dest: No offense intended. I know it's a tough job.

String.Source: That's understandable, but whether you want it or not, the job is yours.
String.Dest: That's understandable, but whether you want it or not, the job is yours.

String.Source: Got some medical supplies, too, if you're looking for those.
String.Dest: Got some medical supplies, too, if you're looking for those.

String.Source: Anyway, I'm the closest thing to a doctor around here. I treat everyone, Raider, trader and traveler alike.
String.Dest: Anyway, I'm the closest thing to a doctor around here. I treat everyone, Raider, trader and traveler alike.

String.Source: I don't really know what I want to do yet.
String.Dest: I don't really know what I want to do yet.

String.Source: You don't know anything about me. I could be a lot worse than he was.
String.Dest: You don't know anything about me. I could be a lot worse than he was.

String.Source: Now, if you need guns or ammo, I'm the one you talk to. And before you ask, yes, everyone pays. Even you.
String.Dest: Now, if you need guns or ammo, I'm the one you talk to. And before you ask, yes, everyone pays. Even you.

String.Source: Like any market, this place needs caps to run. Whether it's for payoffs, bribes, you name it.
String.Dest: Like any market, this place needs caps to run. Whether it's for payoffs, bribes, you name it.

String.Source: Maybe I didn't want to waste the opportunity to tell you how things really are around here.
String.Dest: Maybe I didn't want to waste the opportunity to tell you how things really are around here.

String.Source: Why do I have to pay for this stuff? I'm the Overboss, remember?
String.Dest: Why do I have to pay for this stuff? I'm the Overboss, remember?

String.Source: Well, I'm sure you've got more important stuff to do than talk to me. Or were you here to pick something up?
String.Dest: Well, I'm sure you've got more important stuff to do than talk to me. Or were you here to pick something up?

String.Source: What, you don't think I can handle it?
String.Dest: What, you don't think I can handle it?

String.Source: If I seem a little salty today, it's just because of how things work around here.
String.Dest: If I seem a little salty today, it's just because of how things work around here.

String.Source: I wasn't really looking to become the Overboss of Nuka-World, but I might as well enjoy the benefits of my position.
String.Dest: I wasn't really looking to become the Overboss of Nuka-World, but I might as well enjoy the benefits of my position.

String.Source: I'm not planning to give anyone nightmares.
String.Dest: I'm not planning to give anyone nightmares.

String.Source: But I guess it doesn't really matter what I think, does it? As long as I'm wearing this collar, I'm no better than a slave.
String.Dest: Ale mám pocit, že je opravdu jedno, co si myslím, že? Dokud nosím tenhle obojek, nejsem o nic lepší než otrok.

String.Source: Piss me off, and you'll find out just how scary I can be.
String.Dest: Piss me off, and you'll find out just how scary I can be.

String.Source: You're right, life is wonderful! Thanks so much for opening my eyes!
String.Dest: You're right, life is wonderful! Thanks so much for opening my eyes!

String.Source: Unless you're here to take this collar off me and set me free, I'll assume you need guns or ammo.
String.Dest: Unless you're here to take this collar off me and set me free, I'll assume you need guns or ammo.

String.Source: Hey, it's not my fault things are like this. I just got here.
String.Dest: Hey, it's not my fault things are like this. I just got here.

String.Source: We do all the work, then the gangs reap the rewards. Pretty sweet setup, at least for you.
String.Dest: We do all the work, then the gangs reap the rewards. Pretty sweet setup, at least for you.

String.Source: Well let's just say the situation in Nuka-World has never been what I'd call equitable.
String.Dest: Well let's just say the situation in Nuka-World has never been what I'd call equitable.

String.Source: You're absolutely right, boss. I shouldn't have said that. Was stupid of me.
String.Dest: You're absolutely right, boss. I shouldn't have said that. Was stupid of me.

String.Source: Hey, that makes sense, boss. You haven't been here for very long, after all.
String.Dest: Hey, that makes sense, boss. You haven't been here for very long, after all.

String.Source: For a second there, I thought you might be making a joke. Hell, I even considered laughing.
String.Dest: For a second there, I thought you might be making a joke. Hell, I even considered laughing.

String.Source: You'll see a lot of hard-working people forced to peddle stolen goods to the travelers who come from all over the wasteland.
String.Dest: You'll see a lot of hard-working people forced to peddle stolen goods to the travelers who come from all over the wasteland.

String.Source: Guns, ammo, you know the deal.
String.Dest: Guns, ammo, you know the deal.

String.Source: A little bit of everything, really. General supplies, some components, that kind of thing. So, what can I get for you?
String.Dest: A little bit of everything, really. General supplies, some components, that kind of thing. So, what can I get for you?

String.Source: But then I remembered that it's not a joke at all. It's the truth I live with every day.
String.Dest: But then I remembered that it's not a joke at all. It's the truth I live with every day.

String.Source: I don't really know what to expect.
String.Dest: I don't really know what to expect.

String.Source: Here to stock up? Or just making the rounds?
String.Dest: Here to stock up? Or just making the rounds?

String.Source: Do you complain this much to everyone, or am I just being singled out here?
String.Dest: Do you complain this much to everyone, or am I just being singled out here?

String.Source: Well it's not every day that one of us low-life traders gets to have words with the high and mighty Overboss.
String.Dest: Well it's not every day that one of us low-life traders gets to have words with the high and mighty Overboss.

String.Source: Yeah, but you're a slave with all his limbs still attached. For now.
String.Dest: Yeah, but you're a slave with all his limbs still attached. For now.

String.Source: Got to keep stocked up on supplies, right?
String.Dest: Got to keep stocked up on supplies, right?

String.Source: Hey, boss. Gotta admit, it was good to see Colter go down. He scared the hell out of me. Gave me nightmares.
String.Dest: Hey, boss. Gotta admit, it was good to see Colter go down. He scared the hell out of me. Gave me nightmares.

String.Source: The medicine you need to set yourself free. I've got chems of all kinds for you, boss. Just tell me what you need.
String.Dest: The medicine you need to set yourself free. I've got chems of all kinds for you, boss. Just tell me what you need.

String.Source: So, uh... what do you think? About running Nuka-World, I mean?
String.Dest: So, uh... what do you think? About running Nuka-World, I mean?

String.Source: Thank goodness. I'll sleep a lot better having you in charge.
String.Dest: Thank goodness. I'll sleep a lot better having you in charge.

String.Source: Makes sense to me.
String.Dest: Makes sense to me.

String.Source: In a word, violent. The other Raiders might also tell you that he got a little too comfortable in the position.
String.Dest: In a word, violent. The other Raiders might also tell you that he got a little too comfortable in the position.

String.Source: I guess any one of us would have done the same thing in your situation.
String.Dest: I guess any one of us would have done the same thing in your situation.

String.Source: In any case, he wasn't someone whose bad side I ever wanted to be on.
String.Dest: In any case, he wasn't someone whose bad side I ever wanted to be on.

String.Source: Got plenty of supplies for you, boss.
String.Dest: Got plenty of supplies for you, boss.

String.Source: Damn right. You should thank me. It's not every day I wander out to visit the peasants.
String.Dest: Damn right. You should thank me. It's not every day I wander out to visit the peasants.

String.Source: Yeah? Let me tell you what you're going to see.
String.Dest: Yeah? Let me tell you what you're going to see.

String.Source: Never said it was. Just figured you should know what you're getting into.
String.Dest: Never said it was. Just figured you should know what you're getting into.

String.Source: Unless you want a bullet in the brain, shut the hell up and get back to work.
String.Dest: Unless you want a bullet in the brain, shut the hell up and get back to work.

String.Source: Well, look who it is. Are you here to grace my humble market stand with your presence, oh great boss?
String.Dest: Well, look who it is. Are you here to grace my humble market stand with your presence, oh great boss?

String.Source: Everyone runs out of ammo sooner or later. So, what do you need?
String.Dest: Everyone runs out of ammo sooner or later. So, what do you need?

String.Source: Fine. I've said all I wanted to say anyway.
String.Dest: Fine. I've said all I wanted to say anyway.

String.Source: What do you need today, boss?
String.Dest: What do you need today, boss?

String.Source: If you need supplies, then I'm you're girl.
String.Dest: If you need supplies, then I'm you're girl.

String.Source: What was he like?
String.Dest: What was he like?

String.Source: I didn't choose this. I was just trying not to be killed by a maniac in power armor.
String.Dest: I didn't choose this. I was just trying not to be killed by a maniac in power armor.

String.Source: Buying or browsing?
String.Dest: Buying or browsing?

String.Source: Stocking up for your next raid? Have a look.
String.Dest: Stocking up for your next raid? Have a look.

String.Source: N- no sir. No way would I piss you off, boss. I'm not stupid.
String.Dest: N- no sir. No way would I piss you off, boss. I'm not stupid.

String.Dest: Hej velkej šéfe, pane. Lauren prodává nápoje. Pravděpodobně si s ní budeš chtít promluvit.

String.Source: Back when Colter first took over, he had big ideas, and he made some big promises.
String.Dest: Back when Colter first took over, he had big ideas, and he made some big promises.

String.Source: What?! You serious?
String.Dest: What?! You serious?

String.Source: Around here, backbone's the only thing that'll keep you alive.
String.Dest: Around here, backbone's the only thing that'll keep you alive.

String.Source: You want a drink, or what?
String.Dest: You want a drink, or what?

String.Source: Whatever you say, boss.
String.Dest: Jak je libo, šéfe.

String.Source: So you're one of the traders who was here before the gangs took over?
String.Dest: So you're one of the traders who was here before the gangs took over?

String.Source: I'll tell you what raiders are. They're people who see the true nature of the world, an' they ain't afraid of it.
String.Dest: I'll tell you what raiders are. They're people who see the true nature of the world, an' they ain't afraid of it.

String.Source: You've got some serious backbone.
String.Dest: You've got some serious backbone.

String.Source: Fine, I'll put the damn thing on. I'll even serve you a drink, but I'll still be hopin' you get a knife between the ribs from one of these Raiders.
String.Dest: Fine, I'll put the damn thing on. I'll even serve you a drink, but I'll still be hopin' you get a knife between the ribs from one of these Raiders.

String.Source: You seem pretty well informed about Colter's plans.
String.Dest: You seem pretty well informed about Colter's plans.

String.Source: That, an' the fact I don't take shit from anyone. In here, it's my drinks an' my rules.
String.Dest: That, an' the fact I don't take shit from anyone. In here, it's my drinks an' my rules.

String.Source: Do you think you'll follow through on Colter's plan? Get the juice flowing again?
String.Dest: Do you think you'll follow through on Colter's plan? Get the juice flowing again?

String.Source: You want to stay here? Even though you have to work for Raiders?
String.Dest: You want to stay here? Even though you have to work for Raiders?

String.Source: The answer is, because they got a healthy mix of fear an' respect, that's why.
String.Dest: The answer is, because they got a healthy mix of fear an' respect, that's why.

String.Source: Well, yeah. Colter needed my input on getting the power plant running again.
String.Dest: Well, yeah. Colter needed my input on getting the power plant running again.

String.Source: I assume it's because the gangs trust you not to run off.
String.Dest: I assume it's because the gangs trust you not to run off.

String.Source: Last I heard, those folks were holed up in Dry Rock Gulch. They're probably struggling, if they're alive at all.
String.Dest: Last I heard, those folks were holed up in Dry Rock Gulch. They're probably struggling, if they're alive at all.

String.Source: Speaking of which, do you think you'll see it through? Colter's plan, I mean?
String.Dest: Speaking of which, do you think you'll see it through? Colter's plan, I mean?

String.Source: Of course. We'll do whatever you say.
String.Dest: Of course. We'll do whatever you say.

String.Source: Now what the hell do you want?
String.Dest: Now what the hell do you want?

String.Source: I can see the question in your eyes. Why ain't she got a collar? You want to take a guess?
String.Dest: I can see the question in your eyes. Why ain't she got a collar? You want to take a guess?

String.Source: I don't really give a shit.
String.Dest: I don't really give a shit.

String.Source: You say "Raiders" like they're somethin' worse than normal folks.
String.Dest: You say "Raiders" like they're somethin' worse than normal folks.

String.Source: Now, what I can get you, boss?
String.Dest: Now, what I can get you, boss?

String.Source: His plan was to get the power plant back online and light up the whole park, making it easier to conquer, and safer for all of us.
String.Dest: His plan was to get the power plant back online and light up the whole park, making it easier to conquer, and safer for all of us.

String.Source: New boss, new rules. From now on, you wear your collar.
String.Dest: New boss, new rules. From now on, you wear your collar.

String.Source: That'll be the day! Haha!
String.Dest: That'll be the day! Haha!

String.Source: You're right about that, haha.
String.Dest: You're right about that, haha.

String.Source: Colter had the right idea. I just might finish what he started.
String.Dest: Colter had the right idea. I just might finish what he started.

String.Source: Restoring power sounds like a waste of time. We've already got everything we need right here.
String.Dest: Restoring power sounds like a waste of time. We've already got everything we need right here.

String.Source: Well ain't you a spoilsport.
String.Dest: Well ain't you a spoilsport.

String.Source: What poor bastards are you talking about?
String.Dest: What poor bastards are you talking about?

String.Source: I'm sort of the unofficial chief handyman around here, or as close as we've got to one.
String.Dest: I'm sort of the unofficial chief handyman around here, or as close as we've got to one.

String.Source: Just tell me what you want.
String.Dest: Just tell me what you want.

String.Source: Still... it would be a sight, all these lights coming back on... All the color.
String.Dest: Still... it would be a sight, all these lights coming back on... All the color.

String.Source: Damn right! Hell, I'm an institution.
String.Dest: Damn right! Hell, I'm an institution.

String.Source: Go on now, take a guess why I ain't got a collar.
String.Dest: Go on now, take a guess why I ain't got a collar.

String.Source: Trust? Hell no! A real raider don't trust anyone but himself.
String.Dest: Důvěra? Sakra ne! Skutečný nájezdník nevěří nikomu kromě sebe.

String.Source: If there's a chance that Colter's plans could get this place back on track, I'm interested.
String.Dest: If there's a chance that Colter's plans could get this place back on track, I'm interested.

String.Source: Keep talking, or I'll beat it out of you instead.
String.Dest: Keep talking, or I'll beat it out of you instead.

String.Source: You can keep the collar off. I get the feeling you wouldn't put it on even if I told you to.
String.Dest: You can keep the collar off. I get the feeling you wouldn't put it on even if I told you to.

String.Source: Guess you could say I've got a vested interest in the plan to get the power back on.
String.Dest: Guess you could say I've got a vested interest in the plan to get the power back on.

String.Source: Back when the Raiders took over, some of us - the traders who were here before, I mean - got away.
String.Dest: Back when the Raiders took over, some of us - the traders who were here before, I mean - got away.

String.Source: I hope you do, boss.
String.Dest: I hope you do, boss.

String.Source: No need for that, boss. I'll tell you everything I know.
String.Dest: No need for that, boss. I'll tell you everything I know.

String.Source: We could have done it, too, but things changed. Slowed down. Colter stopped pushing, stopped caring so much.
String.Dest: We could have done it, too, but things changed. Slowed down. Colter stopped pushing, stopped caring so much.

String.Source: Can't stand wearin' this damn thing. What can I get you?
String.Dest: Can't stand wearin' this damn thing. What can I get you?

String.Source: Was hoping you'd come by, boss. You ain't really seen the park 'til you've stopped in for a drink at Cappy's
String.Dest: Was hoping you'd come by, boss. You ain't really seen the park 'til you've stopped in for a drink at Cappy's

String.Source: Guess that means his big plans for the park died with him.
String.Dest: Guess that means his big plans for the park died with him.

String.Source: A dream? Yeah, maybe, but I've got to hold onto something. Most days, that's all I've got.
String.Dest: A dream? Yeah, maybe, but I've got to hold onto something. Most days, that's all I've got.

String.Source: And just imagine... at night, you'd see it for miles around. Folk would talk about it. They'd come from all over to shop in the market.
String.Dest: And just imagine... at night, you'd see it for miles around. Folk would talk about it. They'd come from all over to shop in the market.

String.Source: You're dreaming if you think turning on some lights is going to magically transform this place into something great.
String.Dest: You're dreaming if you think turning on some lights is going to magically transform this place into something great.

String.Source: Gotta get back to work here. See you around, boss.
String.Dest: Gotta get back to work here. See you around, boss.

String.Source: It's your call, boss, but there's plenty of time to figure things out.
String.Dest: It's your call, boss, but there's plenty of time to figure things out.

String.Source: When you put it that way, it does sound like a pretty good idea.
String.Dest: When you put it that way, it does sound like a pretty good idea.

String.Source: Been about twenty years now, I guess. For better or worse, Nuka-World is my home.
String.Dest: Been about twenty years now, I guess. For better or worse, Nuka-World is my home.

String.Source: Hey there, boss. You really laid a beat-down on Colter. That was something.
String.Dest: Hey there, boss. You really laid a beat-down on Colter. That was something.

String.Source: How about you tell about these "big plans," and I'll decide if they're worth pursuing.
String.Dest: How about you tell about these "big plans," and I'll decide if they're worth pursuing.

String.Source: You've wasted enough of my time, scab. Get back to work.
String.Dest: You've wasted enough of my time, scab. Get back to work.

String.Source: That's a lot of caps for you and the gangs.
String.Dest: That's a lot of caps for you and the gangs.

String.Source: How long have you been here?
String.Dest: How long have you been here?

String.Source: Truth is, I've dreamed about that day more than once. Not sure why, really.
String.Dest: Truth is, I've dreamed about that day more than once. Not sure why, really.

String.Source: Whatever you say, boss.
String.Dest: Jak je libo, šéfe.

String.Source: Sounds funny, I know, but I think Nuka-World is something really special. I think she deserves to have her lights shine again.
String.Dest: Sounds funny, I know, but I think Nuka-World is something really special. I think she deserves to have her lights shine again.

String.Source: Maybe I've just grown attached to the place, what with all the work I've done on it.
String.Dest: Maybe I've just grown attached to the place, what with all the work I've done on it.

String.Source: I'll be leaving soon enough.
String.Dest: I'll be leaving soon enough.

String.Source: Meantime, you better watch your back. People who make bad decisions don't last long around here.
String.Dest: Meantime, you better watch your back. People who make bad decisions don't last long around here.

String.Source: Call it preferred status. I get first crack at whatever the gangs bring in. Helps me keep a good stock on hand.
String.Dest: Call it preferred status. I get first crack at whatever the gangs bring in. Helps me keep a good stock on hand.

String.Source: I'll be gone by the time you come back.
String.Dest: I'll be gone by the time you come back.

String.Source: Your serious? Fine. I'll finish up my business here and hit the road.
String.Dest: Your serious? Fine. I'll finish up my business here and hit the road.

String.Source: Exactly. Customers means caps, and caps means everyone's happy. When a bunch of Raiders aren't happy any more, the bullets start flying.
String.Dest: Přesně. Zákazníci znamenají zátky a zátky znamenají, že každý je šťastný. A když nebude banda nájezdníků uspokojená, začnou lítat kulky.

String.Source: Will do.
String.Dest: Provedu.

String.Source: I don't know you, and I don't trust you. I don't want to see you back here.
String.Dest: I don't know you, and I don't trust you. I don't want to see you back here.

String.Source: I don't really need your advice.
String.Dest: I don't really need your advice.

String.Source: Whatever his faults, I'll say this - Colter built something here, something important.
String.Dest: Whatever his faults, I'll say this - Colter built something here, something important.

String.Source: It's a delicate balance, this place. Lot of reward but just as much risk. All I'm saying is, don't let things get out of hand.
String.Dest: It's a delicate balance, this place. Lot of reward but just as much risk. All I'm saying is, don't let things get out of hand.

String.Source: As long as people feel safe coming here, the caps will flow. But Raiders, they're unpredictable. Quick-tempered.
String.Dest: As long as people feel safe coming here, the caps will flow. But Raiders, they're unpredictable. Quick-tempered.

String.Source: Now don't you worry. Even despite that unfortunate incident, I'm still operating at well over sixty-one percent normal capacity.
String.Dest: Now don't you worry. Even despite that unfortunate incident, I'm still operating at well over sixty-one percent normal capacity.

String.Source: I'll run this place however I want.
String.Dest: I'll run this place however I want.

String.Source: Sorry, no offense Just trying to help. After all, if this place prospers, it's good for both of us.
String.Dest: Sorry, no offense Just trying to help. After all, if this place prospers, it's good for both of us.

String.Source: What do you mean?
String.Dest: Co tím myslíš?

String.Source: I'm glad you see it that way.
String.Dest: Jsem ráda, že to tak vidíš.

String.Source: Sounds good to me. Feel free to keep that going.
String.Dest: Sounds good to me. Feel free to keep that going.

String.Dest: Whatever arrangement you've got with Shank is your business.

String.Dest: What are you getting out of this special arrangement?

String.Dest: Since you're here, can I hook you up with any supplies?

String.Dest: Wouldn't be much of a market if we didn't have customers.

String.Source: I'll be hitting the road soon.
String.Dest: I'll be hitting the road soon.

String.Dest: Hello? Anybody home?

String.Source: Well, uh... was that it?
String.Dest: Well, uh... was that it?

String.Source: Feeling alright?
String.Dest: Feeling alright?

String.Dest: Doing alright there, boss?

String.Source: Sorry. I know you didn't ask for this. It's just hard not to be bitter, you know?
String.Dest: Sorry. I know you didn't ask for this. It's just hard not to be bitter, you know?

String.Dest: Something wrong? Decided this Overboss thing isn't for you?

String.Dest: If you have any questions about Nuka-World, I'd be delighted to answer them!

String.Dest: It's the kind of opportunity you don't want to take for granted.

String.Source: Be sure to collect Park Medallions as you enjoy our amazing rides and attractions! There's a special reward if you collect a full set!
String.Dest: Ujistěte se, že sbíráte medailony parku při vychutnávání si našich úžasných jízd a atrakcí! K dispozici je speciální odměna, pokud sesbíráte celou sadu!

String.Source: Figure it must be a pretty tough job, keeping all these Raiders in line.
String.Dest: Figure it must be a pretty tough job, keeping all these Raiders in line.

String.Source: Fortunately, my audio receptors recorded the entire event, and I submitted a holotape per standard security procedures.
String.Dest: Fortunately, my audio receptors recorded the entire event, and I submitted a holotape per standard security procedures.

String.Source: I wish I could say! The personnel involved do not match visual records of any known Nuka-World employees.
String.Dest: I wish I could say! The personnel involved do not match visual records of any known Nuka-World employees.

String.Source: What?! No! That's not what I... I mean, yes, I'm sure you can handle it.
String.Dest: What?! No! That's not what I... I mean, yes, I'm sure you can handle it.

String.Source: Some of the gangs were guessing he got too comfortable, but I don't really know.
String.Dest: Some of the gangs were guessing he got too comfortable, but I don't really know.

String.Source: So, think you're up to the task?
String.Dest: So, think you're up to the task?

String.Source: The way you took on Colter... I don't think there's anything you can't handle, boss.
String.Dest: The way you took on Colter... I don't think there's anything you can't handle, boss.

String.Source: Oh good, I was afraid you might be using questionable ingredients.
String.Dest: Oh good, I was afraid you might be using questionable ingredients.

String.Source: Anything noteworthy happens either here in Nuka-World or out in the Commonwealth, odds are, he's well-informed about it.
String.Dest: Anything noteworthy happens either here in Nuka-World or out in the Commonwealth, odds are, he's well-informed about it.

String.Source: Sounds like he just got comfortable.
String.Dest: Sounds like he just got comfortable.

String.Source: Wait, did you just say Bloodworm Meat?
String.Dest: Wait, did you just say Bloodworm Meat?

String.Source: I'm... uh, sure you know what you're doing.
String.Dest: I'm... uh, sure you know what you're doing.

String.Source: Who is Shank?
String.Dest: Who is Shank?

String.Source: A lot of people come a long way to trade here. A lot of caps flow through the market.
String.Dest: Mnoho lidí má za sebou dlouhou cestu, aby zde mohli obchodovat. Mnoho zátek již proteklo tržnicí.

String.Source: Just like I don't ever want to be on yours.
String.Dest: Just like I don't ever want to be on yours.

String.Source: Fortunately, my audio receptors recorded the entire event, and I submitted a holotape per standard security procedures.
String.Dest: Fortunately, my audio receptors recorded the entire event, and I submitted a holotape per standard security procedures.

String.Source: I think we should keep this place going, like the way it used to be.
String.Dest: I think we should keep this place going, like the way it used to be.

String.Source: You got it.
String.Dest: Jak chceš.

String.Source: My audio receptors recorded the entire event, and I submitted a holotape recording per standard security procedures.
String.Dest: My audio receptors recorded the entire event, and I submitted a holotape recording per standard security procedures.

String.Source: Can't argue with that. If you ask me, they've had it coming for a long time.
String.Dest: Can't argue with that. If you ask me, they've had it coming for a long time.

String.Source: Boss... I... I can't believe it. You killed the Raiders. All of them. I have to ask... why?
String.Dest: Šéfe... Já... Nemůžu tomu uvěřit. Jste zabili nájezdníky. Všechny. Musím se zeptat... proč?

String.Source: You and the other traders were being treated like slaves. I had to put an end to it.
String.Dest: You and the other traders were being treated like slaves. I had to put an end to it.

String.Source: And finally, in celebration of its worldwide debut, we've revamped the World of Refreshment ride to feature a river of Nuka-Cola Quantum!
String.Dest: And finally, in celebration of its worldwide debut, we've revamped the World of Refreshment ride to feature a river of Nuka-Cola Quantum!

String.Source: Internal systems monitoring recorded an unauthorized shutdown and reboot.
String.Dest: Internal systems monitoring recorded an unauthorized shutdown and reboot.

String.Source: Right away, boss.
String.Dest: Right away, boss.

String.Source: Alright.
String.Dest: Dobře.

String.Source: You're right. We need to make that decision for ourselves.
String.Dest: You're right. We need to make that decision for ourselves.

String.Source: Only now, we can use the money we bring in to make our lives better.
String.Dest: Only now, we can use the money we bring in to make our lives better.

String.Source: Whatever you want.
String.Dest: Jak si přeješ.

String.Source: Freedom... I never appreciated that word as much as I do right now.
String.Dest: Freedom... I never appreciated that word as much as I do right now.

String.Source: Oh... okay, boss. I, uh... really hope you've scratched that itch now.
String.Dest: Oh... okay, boss. I, uh... really hope you've scratched that itch now.

String.Source: Wherever the road takes you, know that you'll always be welcomed back here in Nuka-World.
String.Dest: Wherever the road takes you, know that you'll always be welcomed back here in Nuka-World.

String.Source: Sure thing.
String.Dest: Jasňačka.

String.Source: Sure.
String.Dest: Jasně.

String.Source: You bet!
String.Dest: You bet!

String.Source: You know, I think we should keep this market open. Bring it back to what it used to be, a place where everyone feels welcome.
String.Dest: You know, I think we should keep this market open. Bring it back to what it used to be, a place where everyone feels welcome.

String.Source: That's not my problem.
String.Dest: To není můj problém.

String.Source: When functionality was restored, several behavioral parameters had been altered.
String.Dest: When functionality was restored, several behavioral parameters had been altered.

String.Source: Want a commanding view while you enjoy a world-class dining experience? Head on up to the Fizztop Grille on Fizztop Mountain.
String.Dest: Want a commanding view while you enjoy a world-class dining experience? Head on up to the Fizztop Grille on Fizztop Mountain.

String.Source: Okay.
String.Dest: Dobrá.

String.Source: You're right. We need to make that decision for ourselves.
String.Dest: You're right. We need to make that decision for ourselves.

String.Source: Raiders steal and kill without remorse. They don't deserve to live.
String.Dest: Nájezdníci krádou a zabíjejí bez výčitek svědomí. Oni si nezaslouží žít.

String.Source: You got it, boss.
String.Dest: Jasně, šéfe.

String.Source: Now if you'll excuse me, I've got to figure out a way to safely remove these collars.
String.Dest: Now if you'll excuse me, I've got to figure out a way to safely remove these collars.

String.Source: Before you go, there's one last thing I need to say. Thank you. Sincerely, from all of us. Thank you.
String.Dest: Before you go, there's one last thing I need to say. Thank you. Sincerely, from all of us. Thank you.

String.Source: Now that it has, I'm left with a question that I don't know the answer to: What happens next?
String.Dest: Now that it has, I'm left with a question that I don't know the answer to: What happens next?

String.Source: You'll have to figure that out on your own.
String.Dest: You'll have to figure that out on your own.

String.Source: Well, you certainly did that.
String.Dest: Well, you certainly did that.

String.Source: I've thought about this day for a long time. Dreamed about it, really, though I never thought I'd see that dream come true.
String.Dest: I've thought about this day for a long time. Dreamed about it, really, though I never thought I'd see that dream come true.

String.Source: Hey, no problem.
String.Dest: Hey, no problem.

String.Source: Whatever you want, boss.
String.Dest: Whatever you want, boss.

String.Source: Not sure, really. I guess I just felt like killing a lot of people.
String.Dest: Not sure, really. I guess I just felt like killing a lot of people.

String.Source: What do you want to happen?
String.Dest: What do you want to happen?

String.Source: My pleasure.
String.Dest: Bylo mi potěšením.

String.Source: Okay.
String.Dest: Dobrá.

String.Source: You're free now. You can do anything you want.
String.Dest: You're free now. You can do anything you want.

String.Source: Suit yourself.
String.Dest: Posluž si.

String.Source: Alright then.
String.Dest: Dobře teda.

String.Source: No problem.
String.Dest: Žádný problém.

String.Source: I guess not. I'm sure you had your reasons.
String.Dest: I guess not. I'm sure you had your reasons.

String.Source: Does it really matter? You're free now.
String.Dest: Does it really matter? You're free now.

String.Source: Comin' right up!
String.Dest: Comin' right up!

String.Source: The gangs are gone... It's like a weight's been lifted off us. Thanks.
String.Dest: The gangs are gone... It's like a weight's been lifted off us. Thanks.

String.Source: Ammo here. Don't want to be caught without it.
String.Dest: Ammo here. Don't want to be caught without it.

String.Source: Wasteland's a dangerous place. Arm yourself with a quality weapon right here.
String.Dest: Wasteland's a dangerous place. Arm yourself with a quality weapon right here.

String.Source: Used to work because the Raiders made me. Now it's because I really want to make this place better.
String.Dest: Used to work because the Raiders made me. Now it's because I really want to make this place better.

String.Source: General supplies here! Come and stock up!
String.Dest: General supplies here! Come and stock up!

String.Source: Supplies of all kind for your journeys across the Commonwealth.
String.Dest: Supplies of all kind for your journeys across the Commonwealth.

String.Source: Park sure is a sight, what with all the lights on.
String.Dest: Park sure is a sight, what with all the lights on.

String.Source: Without the Raiders making everyone nervous, I think you'll get a lot more visitors here.
String.Dest: Without the Raiders making everyone nervous, I think you'll get a lot more visitors here.

String.Source: The Raiders are gone. They're really gone. I can hardly believe it. Anyway, sorry, what did you need, boss?
String.Dest: Nájezdníci jsou pryč. Jsou opravdu pryč. Nemohu tomu uvěřit. Mimochodem, promiň, cos potřeboval, šéfe?

String.Source: General goods here! Come on over and pick up what you need.
String.Dest: General goods here! Come on over and pick up what you need.

String.Source: Need supplies? Got a little of everything here. Come take a look!
String.Dest: Need supplies? Got a little of everything here. Come take a look!

String.Source: You really did it. You got the power plant up and running and everything.
String.Dest: You really did it. You got the power plant up and running and everything.

String.Source: Hey, boss. Good to see you.
String.Dest: Hey, boss. Good to see you.

String.Source: Guns and ammo here.
String.Dest: Guns and ammo here.

String.Source: Take control of your mind! Fly without wings! I got chems for every need.
String.Dest: Take control of your mind! Fly without wings! I got chems for every need.

String.Source: You really taught those Raiders a lesson.
String.Dest: Díky tobě fakt dostali tihle nájezdníci lekci.

String.Source: I feel a lot better shopping here now that the Raiders are gone.
String.Dest: I feel a lot better shopping here now that the Raiders are gone.

String.Source: No more Raiders... if this is a dream, don't wake me up.
String.Dest: No more Raiders... if this is a dream, don't wake me up.

String.Source: Really cleaned the Raiders out of here, didn't you? Too bad, they were some of my best customers. So, what are you having?
String.Dest: Really cleaned the Raiders out of here, didn't you? Too bad, they were some of my best customers. So, what are you having?

String.Source: Stims, chems and other sweet treats. Get 'em while they last!
String.Dest: Stims, chems and other sweet treats. Get 'em while they last!

String.Source: You really gave those Raiders hell, boss.
String.Dest: You really gave those Raiders hell, boss.

String.Source: Got the power plant back online, huh?
String.Dest: Got the power plant back online, huh?

String.Source: Pistols, rifles, grenades and every other kind of weapon you need.
String.Dest: Pistols, rifles, grenades and every other kind of weapon you need.

String.Source: Ain't nothin' sweeter than freedom, boss. Gotta say, it feels pretty damn good. How can I be of service?
String.Dest: Ain't nothin' sweeter than freedom, boss. Gotta say, it feels pretty damn good. How can I be of service?

String.Source: Weapons of all kinds, yours for a fair price.
String.Dest: Weapons of all kinds, yours for a fair price.

String.Source: Feeling down? I got your pickup right here.
String.Dest: Feeling down? I got your pickup right here.

String.Source: It's a new day, boss. We all owe you one. Now what can I get for you?
String.Dest: It's a new day, boss. We all owe you one. Now what can I get for you?

String.Source: Can't believe you took on all three of those raider gangs. You must be the bravest person in the whole Commonwealth.
String.Dest: Can't believe you took on all three of those raider gangs. You must be the bravest person in the whole Commonwealth.

String.Source: Looking to chill out, or get fired up? Either way, I got what you need.
String.Dest: Looking to chill out, or get fired up? Either way, I got what you need.

String.Source: Of course not, boss.
String.Dest: Of course not, boss.

String.Source: I don't mean any offense, boss. It's just the way things run around here.
String.Dest: I don't mean any offense, boss. It's just the way things run around here.

String.Source: That, and, well... I'd be lying if I said we weren't all wondering how you plan to run the place.
String.Dest: That, and, well... I'd be lying if I said we weren't all wondering how you plan to run the place.

String.Source: Well now, what's this? Got us a celebrity here. It's the queen of the castle herself. The one and only boss of Nuka-World!
String.Dest: Well now, what's this? Got us a celebrity here. It's the queen of the castle herself. The one and only boss of Nuka-World!

String.Source: You could uh, well, you know... get rid of the Raiders if you don't exactly agree with how they're running the place.
String.Dest: You could uh, well, you know... get rid of the Raiders if you don't exactly agree with how they're running the place.

String.Source: When it's all said and done, you're still running this place from your fancy house on the mountain over there.
String.Dest: When it's all said and done, you're still running this place from your fancy house on the mountain over there.

String.Source: Well, I admit, I didn't like being roped into this "job" in the first place.
String.Dest: Well, I admit, I didn't like being roped into this "job" in the first place.

String.Source: How dare you suggest something like that! I should have you shot!
String.Dest: How dare you suggest something like that! I should have you shot!

String.Source: Are you out of your mind?
String.Dest: Zešílel si?

String.Source: Except now, you won't have to sleep with a gun under your pillow.
String.Dest: Except now, you won't have to sleep with a gun under your pillow.

String.Source: I should uh, probably stop talking about this out here. Just keep what I said in mind.
String.Dest: Měla bych... uh, pravděpodobně přestat tady o tom mluvit. Jen si musím zapamatovat to, co jsem právě řekla.

String.Source: If you're serious about this, then you'll have to take down the leaders of the gangs.
String.Dest: If you're serious about this, then you'll have to take down the leaders of the gangs.

String.Source: That means putting a bullet into Nisha, Mason, Mags and Mags's brother, William.
String.Dest: That means putting a bullet into Nisha, Mason, Mags and Mags's brother, William.

String.Source: Once you do that, the gangs will collapse and Nuka-Town goes back to being a free-trading post.
String.Dest: Once you do that, the gangs will collapse and Nuka-Town goes back to being a free-trading post.

String.Source: Got to be something good in here.
String.Dest: Got to be something good in here.

String.Source: Just, hear me out.
String.Dest: Just, hear me out.

String.Source: It's your call, boss.
String.Dest: It's your call, boss.

String.Source: Getting close to something good, I can feel it.
String.Dest: Getting close to something good, I can feel it.

String.Source: The gangs that call this place home are already at each other's throats.
String.Dest: The gangs that call this place home are already at each other's throats.

String.Source: I mean, this is your show now, you can do anything you want. You could run Nuka-World just like Colter... business as usual. Or...
String.Dest: I mean, this is your show now, you can do anything you want. You could run Nuka-World just like Colter... business as usual. Or...

String.Source: Wow. This is the first time I've ever watched someone dig their own grave.
String.Dest: Wow. This is the first time I've ever watched someone dig their own grave.

String.Source: Now you could risk your own neck and try to keep them from tearing each other apart or you could do the right thing and put them in the ground.
String.Dest: Now you could risk your own neck and try to keep them from tearing each other apart or you could do the right thing and put them in the ground.

String.Source: No, of course not.
String.Dest: No, of course not.

String.Source: Caps, ammo, salvage, drugs.. at least some of that's got to be hiding in here.
String.Dest: Caps, ammo, salvage, drugs.. at least some of that's got to be hiding in here.

String.Source: Man, this is a waste of time.
String.Dest: Man, this is a waste of time.

String.Source: Then this might be your chance to make some changes around here.
String.Dest: Then this might be your chance to make some changes around here.

String.Source: Just forget I said anything, okay?
String.Dest: Just forget I said anything, okay?

String.Source: If you come across any Hubologist crazies, just ignore 'em. Told those freaks to stick to their camp.
String.Dest: If you come across any Hubologist crazies, just ignore 'em. Told those freaks to stick to their camp.
